Package: dlbayes
Type: Package
Title: Use Dirichlet Laplace Prior to Solve Linear Regression Problem
        and Do Variable Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Shijia Zhang; Meng Li
Maintainer: Shijia Zhang <zsj27@mail.ustc.edu.cn>
Description: The Dirichlet Laplace shrinkage prior in Bayesian linear regression and variable selection, featuring:
    utility functions in implementing Dirichlet-Laplace priors such as visualization; 
    scalability in Bayesian linear regression; 
    penalized credible regions for variable selection.
